{"tid":713574,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"有線中國組：兩融現危機 傳當局不允許強行平倉","createTime":"2018-06-23T02:36:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-23T03:55:49.000Z","uid":48083,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"f9bda1b93b01da7ea50433d89db39a512a1dfb7d","tid":713574,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:36:57.000Z","msg":"內地股市近日急挫，目前未贖回的股票質押，市值高達 6 萬億元，佔A股一成。<br />\n<br />\n兩融危機再現，上海證監局在本周開始，要求券商每日上報兩融資料。<br />\n<br />\n上次有同樣要求，正正是 2015 年出現的股災。<br />\n<br />\n21 世紀經濟報道，前兩天都有過百客戶瀕臨爆倉，涉及數億元人民幣，形容情況「十分慘烈」。<br />\n<br />\n更有消息指，大額股權質押，要得到中證監同意才能賣出，不允許強行平倉。<br />\n<br />\n#有線新聞　#人民幣　#內地股災　#兩融危機　#平倉潮　#兩融　#股市急挫　#icablenews　#hknews　#cablenews　#newsdaily　#news<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/870652953126774/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ficablenews%2Fvideos%2F870652953126774%2F&d=QtpeFnbj0S7RMojtUuuwcgHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=829afd0b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/icablenews/videos/870652953126774/</a>"},{"pid":"f519edc01feea9789c836f23f8f2ea236d28a9e1","tid":713574,"uid":156652,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:38:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/23/103856_8e99ed5b526c61e3d66173598c5bac59.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F23%2F103856_8e99ed5b526c61e3d66173598c5bac59.gif&h=30c72f16&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a58e6453eb0324a879cb2d19877afec689029ecf","tid":713574,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-23T02:42:21.000Z","msg":"穿左2900 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c63162c3320a0b2e25872905579b29676873f46","tid":713574,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"201